223
00:21:17,291 --> 00:21:18,750
Kenapa kau tidak pergi?

224
00:21:19,333 --> 00:21:21,458
Hindari mereka. Kabur.

225
00:21:21,541 --> 00:21:23,000
Kami harus ke mana?

226
00:21:23,083 --> 00:21:25,458
Ke mana pun yang kau mau.

227
